\begin_layout Standard
"If the primordial prisons are objects that exist both in the real world and
 the time loop reality, doesn't that make them a sort of a… bridge, for the
 lack of a better term?" Zach asked Zorian quietly.
 "If so, it might be possible to use them as a sort of conduit for opening a
 passage between this world and the real one.
 Hell, releasing one of them from their prisons might not even be necessary!"

