"You have?" Zorian asked, leaning forwards with anticipation.
 He had to say, his brother's help was proving itself invaluable when it came
 to jobs like this one.
 If Zach and Zorian had to locate all the missing pieces of the Key all by
 themselves it would have taken them much, much longer than this.
