\begin_layout Standard
"Which is a distinct possibility," Zorian noted.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"At least you have that in-built Key detector, so we'll know if the ring is no
 longer there before we waste too much time on securing the place," Daimen
 shrugged.

