"Of course the damn ring has to be in the most difficult location possible,"
 Zorian grunted unhappily.
 "Just getting there will be an issue."

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"Actually, I think I have a solution to both that and how to reach Blantyrre in
 a reasonable time frame," Daimen grinned before throwing a rolled up poster at
 him.
 "Have a look and tell me what you think."

