\begin_layout Standard
An expensive, experimental airship designed by some of the best artificers in
 Aranhal as part of some kind of national vanity project.
 It was mostly done, the construction crew was just putting finishing touches
 on it currently and it was planned it would undergo a test flight in a few
 weeks.

